An application displays various pages of different page types. To display single, archived or featured articles, articles of a specific category or a list of categories, the different specialized article pages can be used. Beside the typical content representation, particular weblink, newsfeed and contact pages for the representation of the respective content type exist. Users can be represented through user pages. In addition, specialized user pages exist, which display login, register, password reminder and profile edit forms for the user. Another page type is the representation of a search and a smart search form. To display an external web site within an iframe, the iframe wrapper page can be used. Each page can be parameterized through various options.